        <caption>
          <p>Chart showing change in operation over time. The RSS training and independent operators are plotted daily during the transition period (June 2&#x02013;August 18, 2014) and updated periodically, coinciding with subsequent class training for the following 12 mo. The facility staff-operated analysis was historically at 100%, and with the culture change in how end users interact at the facility, this dropped to 40% during the transition, which has persisted for the following 12 mo.</p>
