        </xref> shows year-to-year change in the total number of analysis hours used at the facility from 2010 to 2015. Use of the facility had been changing &#x000b1;5% from 1 yr to the next from 2010 to 2014. With the implementation of independent-user operation, we see a 16.5% increase in overall facility analysis use.
